added.title: Them Soviet Boys
added.description: In order to quickly get through their chores and karate lessons, the Titans learn how to montage

added.title: High Stress Express
added.description: During a live feed of the new transcontinental bullet train, La Grange enters the picture to outrace the train, but Ben joins in on the fun and will stop at nothing to come out on top!

added.title: Can I Keep It?
added.description: After stumbling upon a cute cat-dog-rabbit creature hybrid, or "Cadobbit," Ben ignores Grandpa Max's advice and sneaks the animal onto the Rustbucket, but is quickly in over his head as Dr. Amino's creation turns on him!

added.title: All Koiled Up
added.description: When Ben grows impatient with the snail like pace of gardening, he goes O-E Overflow to pick up the pace and accidentally floods the community garden, but once a giant sink hole appears and frees King Koil and his Kimodo Dragon from below, Ben must quickly right his wrong and capture the baddies if he is to save the coastal city of Bayburgh.

added.title: The Charm Offensive
added.description: After Ben gets too much publicity for his alien antics in Fort Knox, a jealous Gwen feels unappreciated and looks to ease her pain with ice cream, but once she is confronted by Charmcaster looking to avenge Michael Morningstar, Gwen must prove to herself she's a worthy member of Team Tennyson if they are to survive.

added.title: Ye Olde Laser Duel
added.description: As team Tennyson admires the efficiency of a super modern train station, Ben is quick to sniff out one of Steam Smythe's robots holding up the line. Once the fed up villain tricks our hero into accepting a duel, the fate of the Omnitrix hangs in the balance and it's up to Ben to set things right.

added.title: Drone On
added.description: Ben and Gwen are in a highly competitive paper airplane war, but when alien-tech drones bombard the Rustbucket, the cousins must work together to ground the aerial attack and find out who's behind it: the alien conqueror, Vilgax!

added.title: Past Aliens Present
added.description: After Ben stumbles upon a video of Cannonbolt ripping up a computer lab on the internet, Team Tennyson must race to State U to find the imposter; but once Ben discovers it is a steam-punk version of his alien that is terrorizing the campus, Ben must take down the man behind the machine, Steam Smythe!

added.title: Waterfilter
added.description: Ben, Gwen, and Max's trip to Niagara Falls is cut short by the horrid Hydromanders, creatures menacing them and their fellow tourists.

added.title: Riding the Storm Out
added.description: Ben and Gwen's camping trip is interrupted by the emotionless Weatherheads (Gust-o, Hail-o, & Shock-o) but a malfunctioning Omnitrix firing out a mishmash of aliens may not be the forecast for success.

added.title: The Clocktopus
added.description: In a peaceful coastal town, Ben must not only face the archaic antagonist Steam Smythe and his latest creation, the Clocktopus, but also his deepest, darkest fear: Squids!

added.title: Shhh!
added.description: While chilling at a monastery with a no-noise policy, Ben can't keep quiet and accidentally awakens a dangerous Dragon hidden in a secret chamber below the hallowed halls. A job that might be too much for even Diamondhead to handle.

added.title: Animo Farm
added.description: Ben stumbles into Dr. Animo's secret lab now ruled by his superior mutants, the Alphas, and must help the lesser animals escape while stuck as Stinkfly.

added.title: Clown College
added.description: While tailgating at a State U. homecoming football game, Ben teams up with Grandpa Max's old college buddies to keep the crazy clown Zombozo from robbing the stadium blind at halftime.

added.title: Adventures in Babysitting
added.description: Ben, Gwen, and Max meet a family that appears to be a mirror image of them, but when Max goes off on a hike with their matriarch, Maxine, Ben is forced to babysit Simon Sez, a brat with a Billy Billions designed backpack  that turns him into a formidable robot.

added.title: Bright Lights, Black Hearts
added.description: Ben, Gwen, and Max stop by the graveyard set of Gwen's favorite TV show, The Unalivers, but when Ben discovers its lead, Michael Morningstar, is an energy vampire he goes alien to show the world the real star of the show: Heatblast.

added.title: Need for Speed
added.description: Touring Yellowstone, Ben uncovers a plot by the fast & furious LaGrange to find treasure buried below the national park, but with a little help from Old Faithful, Overflow is able to douse LaGrange's dreams.

added.title: Something I Ate
added.description: Ben, Gwen, and Max go on a tour of the impervious Fort Knox, but when Dr. Animo sicks a hungry ani-mutate on the Fort, Ben must stop it before it gobbles up the nation's monitory standard!

added.title: All Wet
added.description: No one believes Ben when he insists that one of the other patrons waiting in line at the World of Wet Water Park is the nefarious Frightwig disguised as a common girl. So Ben must prove his case while protecting park goers from her master plan: to destroy the park with its own water pressure!

added.title: The Attack
added.description: The Ninja celebrate their escape from the Vermillion Army and their retrieval of the Emerald Time Blade but with Acronix and Krux determined to get their Blade back, the Airjitzu Temple becomes a battleground.

added.title: What Was Missing
added.description: Finn & Jake do battle with a powerful door lord.

added.title: Incendium
added.description: Jake sets Finn up with the Flame Princess - with fiery results.

added.title: Animorfosis
added.description: El trío Tennyson excava fósiles de dinosaurio, pero Ben no sabe que Vilgax y el Dr. Animal se complotaron para robar ADN alien del Omnitrix, pero, una vez extraído el ADN, Vilgax traiciona a su cómplice. Ahora Ben debe aliarse con el malvado doctor si quiere tener la oportunidad de derrotar al gran villano. Pero ¿puede confiar en el Dr. Animal?

added.title: Todo Enrollado
added.description: Cuando Ben se impacienta con el ritmo lento de la jardinería, se convierte en O-E Overflow para acelerar las cosas y, por accidente, inunda el jardín de la comunidad.

added.title: Doble Hex
added.description: Mientras observan aves en el Parque Nacional Pinnacles, Gwen y Ben comienzan a competir para ver quién puede avistar más aves primero. Pero cuando el fuego del bosque interrumpe su diversión, el equipo Tennyson debe darse prisa para salvar a la población de aves y descubrir quién está detrás del fuego que crece sospechosamente: iHex!

added.title: El Antiguo Duelo Laser
added.description: Mientras el equipo Tennyson admira la eficiencia de una estación de tren súper moderna, Ben olfatea rápidamente a uno de los robots de Vapor Smythe, que está demorándose más de la cuenta. Pero cuando el villano, harto de esperar, engaña a nuestro héroe para que acepte un duelo, el destino del Omnitrix está en la cuerda floja y Ben es el encargado de arreglar las cosas.

added.title: Toma 10
added.description: Mientras Ben intenta rodar su propia película independiente, por accidente libera a una pandilla de insectos y, cuando la lucha se traslada a su guarida oculta, Ben debe enfrentarse a su líder narcisista: La Hormiga Reina.

added.title: Algo Que Comi
added.description: Ben, Gwen y Max van de paseo al impenetrable Fort Knox, pero cuando el Doctor Ánimo hace que un animal-mutante hambriento se enferme, iBen debe detenerlo antes de que se devore la reserva monetaria de la nación!

added.title: Lectura, Que Aburrido
added.description: Durante una firma de libros en un castillo medieval, Ben debe impedir que Hex se apodere de un grimorio que puede fusionar a su lector con bestias míticas...iy así crear híbridos monstruosos!

added.title: Gwen O Ben
added.description: Cuando Ben interfiere con la misión de Hex -el mago malicioso- para los Titan Gloves, que hacen tareas de movimiento de tierra en un centro de trueque, Hex intercambia el cuerpo de Ben con el de Gwen, lo cual lo obliga a caminar un kilómetro y medio en sus zapatos iy viceversa!

added.title: Ben 24 Horas
added.description: Cuando Ben (iy Gwen!) intenta quedarse despierto toda la noche para ir a Adrenaland -el único parque temático abierto las 24 horas, los siete días de la semana- no solo es incapaz de utilizar sus poderes alienígenas para lograr su objetivo, sino que además su estado de adormecimiento alienígena provoca un desastre tras otro, y Gwen debe arreglar las cosas antes de que todo se salga de control.

added.title: Luces Brillantes, Corazones Oscuros
added.description: Ben, Gwen y Max hacen una parada en el cementerio falso en el que se filma el programa de televisión favorito de Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre que su protagonista, Michael Morningstar, es un vampiro de la energía, se transforma en alienígena para mostrarle al mundo quién es la verdadera estrella del programa: Fuego.

added.title: Olvideti
added.description: Ben, Gwen y Max van de excursión en busca de un Forgeti legendario, un yeti que hace que las personas se olviden de que lo vieron, pero cuando el Doctor Ánimo reúne a los Forgeti para su plan de robar bancos sin que nadie los recuerde, Ben aprende muy pronto que el Forgeti es más que un simple mito.

added.title: Xingo
added.description: Ben está muy interesado en una maratón de Spazz, su dibujo animado favorito, pero cuando se transforma en Upgrade para mejorar la señal de televisión, el protagonista de Spazz salta de su dimensión animada hacia la nuestra...iy trae consigo un caos demente!

added.title: Return to Forever
added.description: The Forever Knights threaten to use a sinister weapon to erase all alien DNA on Earth unless Ben and Rook can stop them.

added.title: Omni-Truco
added.description: Ben debe interrumpir sus vacaciones en Portland cuando descubre un 11mo alien al luchar contra la mega criatura del Dr. Animal. Pero, como la lucha deja a su Omnitrix todo estropeado pasando por los 11 aliens, Max pide ayuda a un viejo amigo para que repare el Omnitrix, que es perseguido por otras fuerzas peligrosas, entre ellas un alien misterioso de la misma especie que el 11mo alien...iVilgax!

added.title: A Fistful of Brains
added.description: Grandpa Max and Rook are looking all over the galaxy for Ben, who is trapped on Khyber's hidden personal hunting preserve.
